[{"id": 559346, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 502, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4511, "text": "Ha, Mim."}, {"id": 559347, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 502, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4512, "text": "Kitab'\u0131n indirilmesi, \u00fcst\u00fcn ve g\u00fc\u00e7l\u00fc, h\u00fck\u00fcm ve hikmet sahibi Allah'tand\u0131r."}, {"id": 559348, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 502, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4513, "text": "Biz g\u00f6kleri, yeri ve ikisi aras\u0131nda bulunanlar\u0131 ancak hak ve ad\u0131 konulmu\u015f bir ecel (belli bir s\u00fcre) olarak yaratt\u0131k. \u0130nkar edenler ise, uyar\u0131ld\u0131klar\u0131 \u015feyden y\u00fcz \u00e7eviren(kimseler)dir."}, {"id": 559349, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 502, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4514, "text": "De ki: \"G\u00f6rd\u00fcn\u00fcz m\u00fc haber verin; Allah'tan ba\u015fka tapt\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131z, yerden neyi yaratm\u0131\u015flar, bana g\u00f6sterin? Yoksa onlar\u0131n g\u00f6klerde bir ortakl\u0131\u011f\u0131 m\u0131 var? E\u011fer do\u011fru s\u00f6zl\u00fcler iseniz, bundan \u00f6nce bir kitap ya da bir ilim kal\u0131nt\u0131s\u0131 (veya bir eser) varsa, bana getirin.\""}, {"id": 559350, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 502, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4515, "text": "Allah'\u0131 b\u0131rak\u0131p k\u0131yamet g\u00fcn\u00fcne kadar kendisine icabet etmeyecek \u015feylere tapandan daha sapm\u0131\u015f kimdir? Oysa onlar, bunlar\u0131n tapmalar\u0131ndan habersizdirler."}, {"id": 559351, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 503, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4516, "text": "\u0130nsanlar ha\u015frolundu\u011fu (biraraya getirildi\u011fi) zaman, (Allah'tan ba\u015fka tapt\u0131klar\u0131) onlara d\u00fc\u015fman kesilirler ve (kendilerine) ibadet etmelerini de tan\u0131mazlar."}, {"id": 559352, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 503, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4517, "text": "Onlara a\u00e7\u0131k belgeler olarak ayetlerimiz okundu\u011fu zaman, o inkar edenler kendilerine gelmi\u015f olan hak i\u00e7in dediler ki: \"Bu, apa\u00e7\u0131k bir b\u00fcy\u00fcd\u00fcr.\""}, {"id": 559354, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 503, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4518, "text": "Yoksa: \"Kendisi onu uydurdu\" mu diyorlar? De ki: \"E\u011fer ben uydurdumsa, bu durumda siz, Allah'tan bana (gelecek) hi\u00e7bir \u015feye malik (engel) olamazs\u0131n\u0131z. Sizin kendisi (Kur'an) hakk\u0131nda, ne ta\u015fk\u0131nl\u0131klar yapt\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 O daha iyi bilendir. Benimle sizin aran\u0131zda \u015fahid olarak O yeter. O, \u00e7ok ba\u011f\u0131\u015flayand\u0131r, \u00e7ok esirgeyendir.\""}, {"id": 559355, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 503, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4519, "text": "De ki: \"Ben el\u00e7ilerden bir t\u00fcredi de\u011filim, bana ve size ne yap\u0131laca\u011f\u0131n\u0131 da bilemiyorum. Ben, yaln\u0131zca bana vahyedilmekte olana uyuyorum ve ben, apa\u00e7\u0131k bir uyar\u0131c\u0131dan ba\u015fkas\u0131 de\u011filim.\""}, {"id": 559356, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 503, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4520, "text": "De ki: \"G\u00f6rd\u00fcn\u00fcz m\u00fc-haber verin; e\u011fer (bu Kur'an,) Allah Kat\u0131ndan ise, siz de onu inkar etmi\u015fseniz ve \u0130srailo\u011fullar\u0131'ndan bir \u015fahid bunun bir benzerine \u015fahidlik edip iman etmi\u015fse ve siz de b\u00fcy\u00fckl\u00fck taslam\u0131\u015fsan\u0131z (bunun sonucu ne olacak)? \u015e\u00fcphesiz Allah, zalim olan bir kavmi hidayete erdirmez."}, {"id": 559357, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 503, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4521, "text": "\u0130nkar edenler, iman edenler i\u00e7in dediler ki: \"E\u011fer O (Kur'an veya iman) hay\u0131rl\u0131 bir \u015fey olsayd\u0131, ona bizden \u00f6nce ko\u015fup-yeti\u015femezlerdi.\" Oysa onlar, onunla hidayete ermediklerinden: \"Bu, eski bir yaland\u0131r\" diyecekler."}, {"id": 559358, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 503, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4522, "text": "Bundan \u00f6nce de, bir rehber (imam) ve bir rahmet olarak Musa'n\u0131n kitab\u0131 var. Bu da, zulmedenleri uyarmak ve ihsanda bulunanlara bir m\u00fcjde olmak \u00fczere (kendinden \u00f6nceki kitaplar\u0131) do\u011frulay\u0131c\u0131 ve Arap\u00e7a bir dil ile olan bir Kitap't\u0131r."}, {"id": 559359, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 503, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4523, "text": "\u015e\u00fcphesiz: \"Bizim Rabbimiz Allah't\u0131r\" deyip sonra do\u011fru bir istikamet tutturanlar (yok mu); art\u0131k onlar i\u00e7in korku yoktur ve onlar mahzun olmayacaklard\u0131r."}, {"id": 559360, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 503, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4524, "text": "\u0130\u015fte onlar, cennet halk\u0131d\u0131r; yapt\u0131klar\u0131na kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131k olmak \u00fczere, i\u00e7inde ebedi olarak kalacaklard\u0131r."}, {"id": 559361, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 504, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4525, "text": "Biz insana, 'anne ve babas\u0131na' iyilikle davranmas\u0131n\u0131 tavsiye ettik. Annesi onu g\u00fc\u00e7l\u00fckle ta\u015f\u0131d\u0131 ve onu g\u00fc\u00e7l\u00fckle do\u011furdu. Onun (hamilelikte) ta\u015f\u0131nmas\u0131 ve s\u00fctten kesilmesi, otuz ayd\u0131r. Nihayet g\u00fc\u00e7l\u00fc (erginlik) \u00e7a\u011f\u0131na erip k\u0131rk y\u0131l (ya\u015f\u0131n)a ula\u015f\u0131nca, dedi ki: \"Rabbim, bana, anne ve babama verdi\u011fin nimete \u015f\u00fckretmemi ve Senin raz\u0131 olaca\u011f\u0131n salih bir amelde bulunmam\u0131 bana ilham et; benim i\u00e7in soyumda salah\u0131 ver. Ger\u00e7ekten ben tevbe edip Sana y\u00f6neldim ve ger\u00e7ekten ben M\u00fcsl\u00fcmanlardan\u0131m.\""}, {"id": 559362, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 504, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4526, "text": "\u0130\u015fte bunlar; yapt\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131n en g\u00fczelini kabul ederiz ve k\u00f6t\u00fcl\u00fcklerinden ge\u00e7eriz; (bunlar) cennet halk\u0131 i\u00e7indedirler. (\u0130\u015fte bu,) Onlara va'dolunan do\u011fru bir vaaddir."}, {"id": 559363, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 504, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4527, "text": "O kimse ki, anne ve babas\u0131na: \"\u00d6f size, benden \u00f6nce nice nesiller gelip ge\u00e7mi\u015fken, beni (diriltilip) \u00e7\u0131kar\u0131laca\u011f\u0131mla m\u0131 tehdit ediyorsunuz?\" dedi. O ikisi (anne ve babas\u0131) ise Allah'a yakararak: \"Yaz\u0131klar sana, iman et, \u015f\u00fcphesiz Allah'\u0131n va'di hakt\u0131r.\" (derler; fakat) O: \"Bu, ge\u00e7mi\u015flerin masallar\u0131ndan ba\u015fkas\u0131 de\u011fildir\" der."}, {"id": 559364, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 504, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4528, "text": "\u0130\u015fte bunlar, cinlerden ve insanlardan kendilerinden evvel gelip-ge\u00e7mi\u015f \u00fcmmetler i\u00e7inde (azap) s\u00f6z\u00fc \u00fczerlerine hak olmu\u015f kimselerdir. Ger\u00e7ekten onlar, ziyana u\u011frayanlard\u0131r."}, {"id": 559365, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 504, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4529, "text": "Her biri i\u00e7in yapt\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131zdan dolay\u0131 dereceler vard\u0131r; \u00f6yle ki amelleri kendilerine eksiksizce \u00f6densin ve onlar zulme de u\u011frat\u0131lmazlar."}, {"id": 559366, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 504, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4530, "text": "\u0130nkar edenler ate\u015fe sunulacaklar\u0131 g\u00fcn, (onlara \u015f\u00f6yle denir:) \"Siz d\u00fcnya hayat\u0131n\u0131zda b\u00fct\u00fcn 'g\u00fczellikleriniz ve zevklerinizi t\u00fcketip-yok ettiniz, onlarla ya\u015fay\u0131p-zevk s\u00fcrd\u00fcn\u00fcz. \u0130\u015fte yery\u00fcz\u00fcnde haks\u0131z yere b\u00fcy\u00fcklenmeniz (istikbar\u0131n\u0131z) ve fas\u0131kl\u0131kta bulunman\u0131zdan dolay\u0131, bug\u00fcn al\u00e7alt\u0131c\u0131 bir azap ile cezaland\u0131r\u0131lacaks\u0131n\u0131z.\""}, {"id": 559367, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 505, "ruku": 440, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4531, "text": "Ad'\u0131n karde\u015fini hat\u0131rla; onun \u00f6n\u00fcnden ve ard\u0131ndan nice uyar\u0131c\u0131lar gelip ge\u00e7mi\u015fti; hani o, Ahkaf'taki kavmini: \"Allah'tan ba\u015fkas\u0131na kulluk etmeyin, ger\u00e7ekten ben, sizin i\u00e7in b\u00fcy\u00fck bir g\u00fcn\u00fcn azab\u0131ndan korkar\u0131m\" diye uyarm\u0131\u015ft\u0131."}, {"id": 559368, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 505, "ruku": 440, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4532, "text": "Dediler ki: \"Sen, bizi ilahlar\u0131m\u0131zdan \u00e7evirmek i\u00e7in mi bize geldin? \u015eu halde e\u011fer do\u011fru s\u00f6yl\u00fcyorsan, tehdit etti\u011fin \u015feyi, bize getir.\""}, {"id": 559369, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 505, "ruku": 440, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4533, "text": "Dedi ki: \"\u0130lim ancak Allah Kat\u0131ndad\u0131r. Ben size g\u00f6nderildi\u011fim \u015feyi tebli\u011f ediyorum; ancak sizi cahillik eden bir kavim olarak g\u00f6r\u00fcyorum.\""}, {"id": 559370, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 505, "ruku": 440, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4534, "text": "Derken, onu (azab\u0131) vadilerine do\u011fru y\u00f6nelerek gelen bir bulut \u015feklinde g\u00f6rd\u00fckleri zaman, \"Bu bize ya\u011fmur ya\u011fd\u0131racak bir buluttur\" dediler. Hay\u0131r, o, kendisi i\u00e7in acele etti\u011finiz \u015feydir. Bir r\u00fczgar; onda ac\u0131 bir azap vard\u0131r."}, {"id": 559371, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 505, "ruku": 440, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4535, "text": "Rabbinin emriyle her\u015feyi yerle bir eder. B\u00f6ylece meskenlerinden ba\u015fka, hi\u00e7bir \u015fey(leri) g\u00f6r\u00fcnemez duruma d\u00fc\u015ft\u00fcler. \u0130\u015fte Biz, su\u00e7lu-g\u00fcnahkar bir kavmi b\u00f6yle cezaland\u0131r\u0131r\u0131z."}, {"id": 559373, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 505, "ruku": 440, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4536, "text": "Andolsun, Biz onlar\u0131, sizleri kendisinde yerle\u015fik k\u0131lmad\u0131\u011f\u0131m\u0131z yerlerde (size vermedi\u011fimiz g\u00fc\u00e7 ve iktidar imkanlar\u0131yla) yerle\u015fik k\u0131ld\u0131k ve onlara i\u015fitme, g\u00f6rme (duygular\u0131n\u0131) ve g\u00f6n\u00fcller verdik. Ancak ne i\u015fitme, ne g\u00f6rme (duyular\u0131) ve ne g\u00f6n\u00fclleri kendilerine herhangi bir \u015fey sa\u011flamad\u0131. \u00c7\u00fcnk\u00fc onlar, Allah'\u0131n ayetlerini inkar ediyorlard\u0131. Alay konusu edindikleri \u015fey, onlar\u0131 sar\u0131p-ku\u015fatt\u0131."}, {"id": 559374, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 505, "ruku": 441, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4537, "text": "Andolsun, Biz \u00e7evrenizde bulunan \u015fehirlerden (bir\u00e7o\u011funu) y\u0131k\u0131ma u\u011fratt\u0131k ve belki d\u00f6nerler diye ayetleri \u00e7e\u015fitli \u015fekillerde a\u00e7\u0131klad\u0131k."}, {"id": 559375, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 505, "ruku": 441, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4538, "text": "Bu durumda, Allah'\u0131 b\u0131rak\u0131p yak\u0131nl\u0131k (sa\u011flamak) i\u00e7in edindikleri ilahlar, onlara yard\u0131m etselerdi ya. Hay\u0131r, onlar, kendilerinden kaybolup gittiler. Bu (yalanc\u0131 ilahlar ve onlara y\u00fckledikleri), onlar\u0131n yalanlar\u0131 ve uydurduklar\u0131d\u0131r."}, {"id": 559376, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 506, "ruku": 441, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4539, "text": "Hani cinlerden birka\u00e7\u0131n\u0131, Kur'an dinlemek \u00fczere sana y\u00f6neltmi\u015ftik. B\u00f6ylece onun huzuruna geldikleri zaman, dediler ki: \"Kulak verin;\" sonra bitirilince kendi kavimlerine uyar\u0131c\u0131lar olarak d\u00f6nd\u00fcler."}, {"id": 559377, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 506, "ruku": 441, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4540, "text": "Dediler ki: \"Ey kavmimiz, ger\u00e7ekten biz, Musa'dan sonra indirilen, kendinden \u00f6ncekileri do\u011frulayan bir Kitap dinledik; hakka ve do\u011fru olan yola y\u00f6neltip-iletmektedir.\""}, {"id": 559378, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 506, "ruku": 441, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4541, "text": "\"Ey kavmimiz, Allah'a davet edene icabet edin ve O\u2019na iman edin; g\u00fcnahlar\u0131n\u0131zdan bir k\u0131sm\u0131n\u0131 ba\u011f\u0131\u015flas\u0131n ve sizi ac\u0131 bir azaptan korusun.\""}, {"id": 559379, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 506, "ruku": 441, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4542, "text": "\"Kim Allah'a davet edene icabet etmezse, art\u0131k o, yery\u00fcz\u00fcnde (Allah'\u0131 aciz b\u0131rakacak de\u011fildir ve onun O'ndan ba\u015fka) velileri yoktur. \u0130\u015fte onlar, apa\u00e7\u0131k bir sap\u0131kl\u0131k i\u00e7indedirler.\""}, {"id": 559380, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 506, "ruku": 441, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4543, "text": "Onlar g\u00f6rm\u00fcyorlar m\u0131 ki, g\u00f6kleri ve yeri yaratan ve onlar\u0131 yaratmaktan yorulmayan (Allah), \u00f6l\u00fcleri de diriltmeye g\u00fc\u00e7 yetirir. Hay\u0131r; ger\u00e7ekten O, her\u015feye g\u00fc\u00e7 yetirendir."}, {"id": 559381, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 506, "ruku": 441, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4544, "text": "\u0130nkar edenler ate\u015fe sunulacaklar\u0131 g\u00fcn, (onlara \u015f\u00f6yle denir:) \"Bu ger\u00e7ek de\u011fil miymi\u015f?\" Onlar: \"Rabbimiz'e andolsun, evet (\u00f6yledir)\" derler. (Allah da:) \"\u00d6yleyse inkar ettiklerinizden dolay\u0131 azab\u0131 tad\u0131n\" dedi."}, {"id": 559382, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 506, "ruku": 441, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4545, "text": "Art\u0131k sen sabret; Resullerden azim sahiplerinin sabrettikleri gibi, Onlar i\u00e7in de acele etme. Onlar, tehdit edildikleri \u015feyi (azab\u0131) g\u00f6rd\u00fckleri g\u00fcn, sanki g\u00fcnd\u00fcz\u00fcn yaln\u0131zca bir saati kadar ya\u015fam\u0131\u015f(olacak)lard\u0131r. (Bu,) Bir tebli\u011fdir. Art\u0131k fas\u0131k olan bir kavimden ba\u015fkas\u0131 y\u0131k\u0131ma u\u011frat\u0131l\u0131r m\u0131?"}]